<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] was a professional assassin. [PAWN_pronoun] was cold, calculating, and made a good profit. In this business, an utter lack of empathy was an asset. -->
  <Assassin20.baseDesc>[PAWN_nameDef]是一名職業殺手。[PAWN_pronoun]冷酷、慎重而且能獲得非常不錯的報酬。在這門生意裡，缺乏同理心是一種資產。</Assassin20.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: assassin -->
  <Assassin20.title>刺客</Assassin20.title>
  <!-- EN: assassin -->
  <Assassin20.titleShort>刺客</Assassin20.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] was used for [PAWN_possessive] body by hundreds of customers in brothels on several planets. [PAWN_pronoun] gained some mental marks and a special kind of street smarts. -->
  <Gigolo30.baseDesc>[PAWN_nameDef]用[PAWN_pronoun]的身體在幾個星球的妓院裡服務了幾百個客戶。雖然因此造成一些心理創傷，卻也讓[PAWN_pronoun]學到某種特殊的街頭智慧。</Gigolo30.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: gigolo -->
  <Gigolo30.title>性工作者</Gigolo30.title>
  <!-- EN: gigolo -->
  <Gigolo30.titleFemale>性工作者</Gigolo30.titleFemale>
  <!-- EN: courtesean -->
  <Gigolo30.titleShort>性工作者</Gigolo30.titleShort>
  <!-- EN: courtesean -->
  <Gigolo30.titleShortFemale>性工作者</Gigolo30.titleShortFemale>
  
  <!-- EN: There is a law that says that you're not allowed to put terawatt-range grasers on a cargo scow. Especially if you hide them under what looks like a communications dish for better ambush potential. [PAWN_nameDef] discovered that there is great profit to be made, however, from those who are uninterested in these laws. -->
  <IllegalShipwright76.baseDesc>有條法律規定不許兆瓦級的光束武器安裝在民用貨船上。特別是你把船埋伏在貨船航線上最佳的伏擊地點時。然而，[PAWN_nameDef]發現能從那些無視法律的人身上大撈一筆。</IllegalShipwright76.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: illegal shipwright -->
  <IllegalShipwright76.title>非法造船匠</IllegalShipwright76.title>
  <!-- EN: shipwright -->
  <IllegalShipwright76.titleShort>造船匠</IllegalShipwright76.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] was nine years old when [PAWN_pronoun] got in [PAWN_possessive] first fight. [PAWN_pronoun] won, but more important was the enjoyment of [PAWN_possessive] audience. Pit fighting turned out to be a lucrative career for those who could survive it. And it was even mostly legal. -->
  <PitBrawler76.baseDesc>[PAWN_nameDef]在[PAWN_pronoun]九歲時第一次打架，而且贏了，但更重要的是[PAWN_pronoun]享受這個過程。地下格鬥對那些能夠生存下去的人來說是個有利可圖的職業，這甚至是合法的。</PitBrawler76.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: pit brawler -->
  <PitBrawler76.title>地下拳擊手</PitBrawler76.title>
  <!-- EN: brawler -->
  <PitBrawler76.titleShort>拳擊手</PitBrawler76.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] was a warrior in an Imperial navy. [PAWN_possessive] job was to punch into enemy starships, gun down the crew, and capture the ship intact. And [PAWN_pronoun] was good at it. -->
  <SpaceMarine16.baseDesc>[PAWN_nameDef]曾是帝國艦隊的戰士。[PAWN_possessive]任務是突入敵艦、放倒船員然後完整的俘虜星艦。而且[PAWN_pronoun]對此十分上手。</SpaceMarine16.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: space marine -->
  <SpaceMarine16.title>太空陸戰隊</SpaceMarine16.title>
  <!-- EN: marine -->
  <SpaceMarine16.titleShort>陸戰隊員</SpaceMarine16.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: Piracy appears everywhere that governments are weak and society spread thin. [PAWN_nameDef] was part of this age-old part of human existence, extorting and smashing peaceful trade ships for profit. -->
  <SpacePirate55.baseDesc>海賊橫行世界，然而政府和社會卻無力控制。[PAWN_nameDef]是這人類古老職業的一分子，為了利益掠奪和摧毀商船。</SpacePirate55.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: space pirate -->
  <SpacePirate55.title>宇宙海賊</SpacePirate55.title>
  <!-- EN: pirate -->
  <SpacePirate55.titleShort>海賊</SpacePirate55.titleShort>
  
</LanguageData>